enhanced_by.reason: Before withdrawing assets, it is necessary to verify the current asset details of the managed sub-account to ensure the withdrawal amount is valid.
Depositing assets into the managed sub-account should occur before attempting to withdraw, ensuring the account has sufficient funds.
After withdrawing assets, verifying the updated asset details of the managed sub-account can confirm the success of the withdrawal operation.
Checking the transfer history can provide additional verification that the withdrawal was recorded correctly.
